org.openpnp.spi

Interface Locatable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Actuator, Camera, HeadMountable, Movable, Nozzle, PasteDispenser, ReferenceHeadMountable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractActuator, AbstractCamera, AbstractNozzle, AbstractPasteDispenser, BufferedImageCamera, HttpActuator, ImageCamera, OnvifIPCamera, OpenCvCamera, OpenPnpCaptureCamera, ReferenceActuator, ReferenceCamera, ReferenceNozzle, ReferencePasteDispenser, SimulatedUpCamera, Webcams

    public interface Locatable
    An object which has a Location in 4D space. The Location may be fixed or Movable. The caller of this method becomes the owner of the returned object and may modify the Location. The returned object should be a clone or copy of the object if modification of it will adversely affect the callee.
